Package: packer
Title: An Opinionated Framework for Using JavaScript with R
Version: 0.0.2.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "John",
           family = "Coene",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jcoenep@gmail.com")
Description:
  Enforces good practice and provides convenience functions to make work with 'JavaScript' 
  not just easier but also scalable. It is a robust wrapper for 'NPM' and 'webpack' that 
  enables to modularise JavaScript code, leverage 'NPM' packages, and much more.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
